name: Josiah Johnson
text:
I ordered over the phone and the CSR was friendly and helpful. They had my food ready in 15 minutes. The pizza was tasty. Overall I suggest this location.
My only complaint is that when getting the 3 topping pizza, extra cheese did not qualify as a topping unlike Domino's.
